Side Effects: It got labor going_ fast and strong. I think labor would have been less painful if this drug hadn't  been used. My water broke but I didn't progress beyond the 1 cm dilation I arrived at the hospital with - until this med was introduced. Then_ boom_ I progressed. From start to finish I had my baby within 8 hours. It was a first labor too. They're supposed to go slowly.
Comments: Painful contractions_ too strong. But effective med for what it was given.
